{
  "stem": "12491.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Fortunately, it wasn't-- it was not I.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When-- when they found out, in the airport, that the ghetto is going to be liquidated within a week, the colonel sent back the buggy, and the horse, and the buggy, and the soldier with the straw, and I was taken back to the airport.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And within the next two, three days-- actually, two days later, all the people in the hospital were distributed poison, and they poisoned themselves because they were to be killed by the SS, not transported to the-- to the Plaszow camp.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Eventually, I was in the airport, and recovered, and I continued my job.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not at the airport.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well-- well, once in a while when they needed some people who-- for a job which had no specific designation, there were no people to do it, they looked through the group of people or group of Jews, and the picked some.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All right, today you will be shoveling coal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was not my assignment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My assignment was to the fur shop.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was still with my brother at this time, yes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We lived-- lived in barracks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had bunk beds, not-- not shelves like they do in concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were given decent amount of food, and by comparison were doing well.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One day the SS came in and decided to paint whatever we were wearing-- we had only one set of clothing-- whatever we were wearing they decided to paint stripes on.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you were wearing a jacket and a pair of pants, and they painted yellow stripes on it so that you would be recognized if you escape.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I believe they, at the same time, gave us the numbers.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
